But I look back at 2021 me, and then I realise "that me" never had dreams as big as the me of today.
2021 me dreamt of "making a cool game with my favourite characters". That was it. Nothing specific.
And you know what? They may have not been very big or even very good games, but...
I've made like, 15 of those now. Check my itch.io! Some of them even with teams.
I've achieved the goals of 2021 me. Why shouldn't I be able to achieve the goals of 2026 me?
I'm not as fast as my peers, but I'm still moving.
